snippet.title: Red Supreme [Visual novel game]
snippet.description:
The world ends in three days, and you, as a devoted cultist, must bring a new member to the cult. Find a balance between the cult, relationships, and job.

Wishlist here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3466180/Red_Supreme/
